title: ound On: TX Dems in DC, Cuba, Infrastructure

description:
Guest hosts Jack Fitzpatrick and Emily Wilkins spoke to Wendy Benjaminson, Bloomberg Washington Deputy Managing Editor, Texas Democratic Party Chairman Gilbert Hinojosa, Bloomberg Businessweek National Political Correspondent Josh Green, Florida Congressman Mario Diaz-Balart and Bloomberg Politics contributors Rick Davis and Jeanne Sheehan Zaino.
